summary: Increases the Unarmed damage for all races to 25.
descriptionHtml:
This mod increases the unarmed damage to 25. By default the Races unarmed damage was 4 for the humans and elves, and 10 for the Khajiit and Argonian.

This plugin needs to (At least for me) be loaded at the bottom of your load order for it to work. If anyone knows how to make it so it works on any load order then message me!


***If you want to improve upon this plugin go for it. 
**Also if you want the unarmed damage decreased let me know and I\'ll make a separate plugin with the new values. 



But if it works for you regardless of load order then disregard what i said.
author: DataRomance
